{"tid":1359490,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（打和）元朗727 | 勇武同和理非 一體化！","createTime":"2019-07-24T06:54:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T10:37:08.000Z","uid":60231,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d7ba588e3fab1014247c515420edf504364162a2","tid":1359490,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:54:09.000Z","msg":"好多5毛帶風向，好多人自己動搖，好多人想說服大家喺打同唔打入面2揀1<br />\n<br />\n但其實，到左今時今日，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非同勇武係冇實際衝突！</span></strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n和理非同勇武，本身就一種因時制易既心態，而唔係一個固定行為<br />\n<br />\n27號照樣齊裝入元朗，照叫口號屌中共屌林鄭屌狗屌黑，有咁大聲得咁大聲，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">盡情言語上侮辱班鄉黑，用民意落佢地面</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果班鄉黑係龜縮唔出，就一路嘈，嘈到自己走嗰一刻，要元朗嘈足成日/兩日，<strong><ins><em>千祈唔好主動攻擊任何人同物</em></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班黑一進攻，和理非即刻轉做勇武自衛心態<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔駛再理公民拘捕權！</strong></span></span> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><em>因為班狗同律政處必定唔會理你！</em></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所有齊裝既人，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">為自己同其他人條命，有幾盡做幾盡！</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n唔係要制止鄉黑行兇，而係，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">優先目標：<ins>確保行兇者失去意識，然後逃走自保</ins></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n所以和理非同勇武需要<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一體化</span></ins></strong>，靜若處子 動若脫兔 <span style=\"color: pink;\"><ins>絕不落單</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n冇人搞你就和理非，有人搞你就即變勇武<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">記住：香港已經冇法治，你唔郁手都可以告你屈你任何罪名</span></span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n所以如果真係被狗睇中，你犯唔犯法，都只係死路一條，E個就係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>TO DO, OR NOT TO DO, 你會點揀？</strong><br />\n<br />\n祝大家冇穿冇爛！"},{"pid":"df9074a42a0a285d7d19cea30020aa7fe6f45104","tid":1359490,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:55:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c82026c4d031ba81b05101a5a6c41461c6ff2e","tid":1359490,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:56:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd47242063d59302f0929f15eef60731694e65e5","tid":1359490,"uid":77820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7a9K01G.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7a9K01G.gif&h=2f1ad75c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無預警下由上而下開槍點計？"},{"pid":"fd6e78656bb4afc203a7eaeef0d1b57ec0db78b8","tid":1359490,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd47242063d59302f0929f15eef60731694e65e5","tid":1359490,"uid":77820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7a9K01G.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7a9K01G.gif&h=2f1ad75c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無預警下由上而下開槍點計？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T06:58:31.000Z","msg":"單單都要跟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但元朗都要入"},{"pid":"bada1be91f1abdb772fe012727dbb26f25521d26","tid":1359490,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69752e02661fe42f9631267bef820d3eaab2fa9","tid":1359490,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d526e9e499b8e29ecac9cac0ff27c96529da737c","tid":1359490,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb038fe5fee99e65a9cafe678695ae52aba4fa17","tid":1359490,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0181b7631ccff8c788c27a3c811b01c2b33db9","tid":1359490,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:08:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4138c2fa158c65261b4abcc279371756b685d95","tid":1359490,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b0181b7631ccff8c788c27a3c811b01c2b33db9","tid":1359490,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:08:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"共鐵必須清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4cba63d6248ac4bd6d9986fccb54fb15b2cb6dd","tid":1359490,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:13:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3faf1dd2409b8a432bf479386619661938d4e245","tid":1359490,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:14:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"94d3b112458004055969b9bf6fcacd63923a113a","tid":1359490,"uid":74021,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:16:04.000Z","msg":"我都好嬲好想打，但打解決唔到問題，而家就有一班平時唔理政治既人出黎鬧政府，正正係因為暴力而企出黎，你以暴制暴於事無補<br />\n<br />\n老黑都係收錢做野，最仆街係何妖，警犬，政府。白衫唔係黎自同一條村，燒村都冇用<br />\n<br />\n何妖明顯玩大左，自己人都唔妥佢，老黑都係收錢先出黎做野，你唔入村打人，佢地得撚閒理你咩。唔好唔記得上水，只要唔搞佢地，避開一啲地方唔去，佢地都唔會搞我地，唔好自亂陣腳<br />\n<br />\n唔好主動郁手，黑社會俾你打完唔還拖仲係黑社會？下次只會打得仲離譜，唔好主動郁手，於事無補<br />\n<br />\n727要人，唔係要武力，要自衛要智取"},{"pid":"0239707361bca52a7f85511ac0e913c5acc6510d","tid":1359490,"uid":60231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3faf1dd2409b8a432bf479386619661938d4e245","tid":1359490,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quo